### Listar alunos
GET http://localhost:8000/alunos

### Criar turma
POST http://localhost:8000/turmas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Turma X",
  "capacidade": 15
}

### Criar aluno
POST http://localhost:8000/alunos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Teste Aluno",
  "data_nascimento": "2014-05-01",
  "email": "teste.aluno@example.com",
  "status": "inativo"
}

### Matricular
POST http://localhost:8000/matriculas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "aluno_id": 1,
  "turma_id": 1
}

### Export CSV
GET http://localhost:8000/export/alunos?format=csv

### Export JSON
GET http://localhost:8000/export/alunos?format=json

### Export Matriculas CSV
GET http://localhost:8000/export/matriculas?format=csv

### Export Matriculas JSON
GET http://localhost:8000/export/matriculas?format=json

### Atualizar aluno
PUT http://localhost:8000/alunos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Teste Aluno Editado",
  "data_nascimento": "2012-06-01",
  "email": "teste.aluno@example.com",
  "status": "ativo",
  "turma_id": 1
}

### Deletar aluno
DELETE http://localhost:8000/alunos/1

### Login (obter token)
POST http://localhost:8000/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=adminpass

### Criar turma (protegido) - incluir header Authorization: Bearer <token>
POST http://localhost:8000/turmas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "nome": "Turma Protected",
  "capacidade": 12
}

### Atualizar turma (protegido)
PUT http://localhost:8000/turmas/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "nome": "Turma Atualizada",
  "capacidade": 20
}

### Deletar turma (protegido)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/turmas/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>
